CM_ SG_ 2527679773 DLM_BFS_HeartbeatCnt "This counter increments each 1s from 1 to 15 and then restart the counting. Value 0 is allowed only after electrical reset, passenger side Signal receivers can detect DLM communication issues thanks to this signal.";
