CM_ SG_ 2527679772 DLM_FS_WDSMActuationsResetTrig "Trigger sent by the replaced DLM in order to ask the other (passenger) side DLM to send the backup value of WDSM actuations. Value is then internally restored";
CM_ SG_ 2527679772 DLM_FS_WDSMStatus "Signal is set to 'Life Cycle Expired' when a prefixed time is elapsed from the WDSM installation with its basic setting.
It is set to 'Discharged' when capacitors voltage is too low.
'Life Cycle Expired' state has priority over 'Discharged'
